## What happened

I started my Flutter project in one window while switching to my Spring Boot + Angular project in another window. That's when this IDE error occurred. It asked me to file a bug, so I did.

It may be the same as https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/5352.

## Version information

- IntelliJ IDEA `2021.1` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 55.0.5` • Dart plugin `211.6693.108`
- No Flutter sdk configured.
- IntelliJ IDEA 2021.1 (Ultimate Edition), Build #IU-211.6693.111, Runtime version: 11.0.10+9-b1341.35 x86_64
- macOS Big Sur 11.2.3

comment_data.body:
Duplicate of https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/5376

It would help us to get some logs (process described here: https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/5376#issuecomment-815384003), so if you have time please post there!
